@DueQ.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5054

### Get settings
GET {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/settings
Accept: application/json

### Update settings
PUT {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "yourName": "Quinntyne Brown",
  "partnerName": "Sam"
}

### List bills
GET {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bills

### Create bill
POST {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Groceries — Loblaws",
  "amount": 84.20,
  "date": "2026-05-22",
  "note": null
}

### Record payment
POST {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 140.00,
  "date": "2026-05-24",
  "method": 0,
  "note": null
}

### Dashboard
GET {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard

### History
GET {{DueQ.Api_HostAddress}}/api/history
